name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: LN.FO The Web Site Content Explainer Info

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: We evaluate websites and keep you safe

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This plugin allows you to surf the Internet safely. When you search on Google, you will find a short information about the sites immediately under the search result. If you want, you can see details about the links you hover over and if the link is dangerous when going to a link, you can turn on the feature to receive a warning before you are directed.
Our aim is that you can browse the internet safely.
